data.description: 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom concrete block home with a metal roof, perfect for those seeking a project to make their own. The property boasts a fully fenced front and back yard, great pets! Enjoy the convenience of the carport, which offers protection for your vehicles and extra storage space. Inside, you'll find a separate dining area and a cozy family room, providing ample space for gatherings and quality time with loved ones. Recent upgrades to one of the bathrooms and part of the kitchen add a touch of modernity, making it an attractive option for those seeking contemporary comfort. Notably, the absence of any carpet throughout the home offers easy maintenance and a clean, contemporary feel. While some areas may need some tender loving care, the property presents an exceptional opportunity for those looking to add their personal touch and create their ideal living space. The solid structure and recent upgrades make it a promising investment. Don't miss out on this chance to transform this property into your perfect haven in this welcoming community."
